commit message: Merge branches 'beta', 'gh-pages' and 'master' of https://github.com/JusticeRage/ApkTrack into beta

Added a function to try and guess the best update source based on the app's signature (#41). Credit goes to @DJaeger for this great idea.
This only works for newly installed apps, pre-existing source choices are not overwritten.

2.0 release of ApkTrack!
The codebase has been mostly rewritten. The list of all changes is described in changelog.txt.
Fixed, use space instead of tab

Merge pull request #73 from precla/master

Updated croatian translation. (From @precla.)

Simplified the project's directory structure.
Fixed a problem causing Toast messages not to appear.
Local project files removed for good.

Updated README.md.
Restored the CNAME file for apktrack.org.
Gradle build will not fail anymore on Lint errors.
Removed `valued-id`, deprecated in favor of `values-in`.
